{"id": "1481968778647437453", "channel_id": "1481968778647437453", "type": 0, "author_id": "396365366298935307", "author_name": "chillercroc", "author_bot": false, "content": "Previously, Light said that aside from GTulu, there wouldn't be more than 2 males this year because the narrative plotline wouldn't allow for it. But how come the same narrative allows for two crossovers?\nThere are also characters who have no ties to the main plot who got released already since then, but at least some loose connections could be made with those. It just kinda sounds like an excuse to keep releasing waifus. Also, how come most of the girls released since Thais are just conventionally attractive waifus with little to no monstrous features at all? Morimens had stood out from the sea of other gachas by how unique and creative their designs were, but now it's just hot girl after hot girl after hot girl. Are there plans to change this any time soon?", "timestamp": "2026-03-13T10:54:50.478000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "Brown_think", "emoji_id": "1459080117308620996", "count": 6}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1481970812662583420", "channel_id": "1481968778647437453", "type": 0, "author_id": "702167871144591461", "author_name": "_venush", "author_bot": false, "content": "About the conventionally attractive waifus\nThe first 4 units they introduced to you, 2 are normal looking girls (Ramona, Lotan).\nThe first Ultra limited is a normal looking woman, most people don’t even realize her torso is hollow.\nThe first Caro limited is a normal looking woman, the 2nd Caro limited is a normal looking man (most people don’t even know he has a tail)\nUltra standards all fall into this, Casiah Liz Winkle, Jenkin only has a fake looking set of ears, Tinct is just purple\nThe more unconventionally ones are much rarer, if not Faros won’t be a standard\nXu is the best case of using human design to enhance the horror experience in the story\n\nThe more normal human looking has always been a part of the game", "timestamp": "2026-03-13T11:02:55.425000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1481971049372586094", "channel_id": "1481968778647437453", "type": 0, "author_id": "702167871144591461", "author_name": "_venush", "author_bot": false, "content": "There are valid criticisms about new design like Vortice but I won’t call all of them that", "timestamp": "2026-03-13T11:03:51.861000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1481971280835117148", "channel_id": "1481968778647437453", "type": 0, "author_id": "702167871144591461", "author_name": "_venush", "author_bot": false, "content": "And Mouchette story is set in arc 2 btw", "timestamp": "2026-03-13T11:04:47.046000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1481972890437156874", "channel_id": "1481968778647437453", "type": 19, "author_id": "396365366298935307", "author_name": "chillercroc", "author_bot": false, "content": "It had more of the monstrous looking ones though. Arc 2 girls so far are all just normal girls, sometimes with different coloration. GDoll is kind of an exception, but even then it's nowhere near the level of, say, 24 or Daffodil with her subtle but still very present unsettling themes. But Kathi, Corposant, GMurphy, Xu, and Vortice are all just normal waifus. Clem gets somewhat of a pass because at least she has weird legs, but it's just overall kind of a letdown.", "timestamp": "2026-03-13T11:11:10.805000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["702167871144591461"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1481970812662583420", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1481973146851610744", "channel_id": "1481968778647437453", "type": 19, "author_id": "396365366298935307", "author_name": "chillercroc", "author_bot": false, "content": "But it has no bearing on the story, which is what they said prevents them from making male characters. You can always make a side story that's set during main plot while having no bearing on it. Making that exception for crossover characters and hot ladies while claiming that you can't do it for male characters is just kind of strange imo.", "timestamp": "2026-03-13T11:12:11.939000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["702167871144591461"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1481971280835117148", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
