{"id": "1481976052166426726", "channel_id": "1481968778647437453", "type": 19, "author_id": "396365366298935307", "author_name": "chillercroc", "author_bot": false, "content": "Production capacity only determines how many total characters can be released, so the decision on which characters to release is based on story planning. So it just feels weird to see the story planning used as a reason they cannot have male characters when the same story planning apparently allows for multiple crossovers and multiple characters with no ties to the main story.", "timestamp": "2026-03-13T11:23:44.620000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1481975491245244518", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
